x125.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/EncoderConnections-768x640.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 479px) 100vw, 479px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Now connect the left and right <strong>Limit Switches<\/strong> as shown:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><a href=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/LimitSwitchesCable.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/LimitSwitchesCable.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2091\" width=\"447\" height=\"348\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/LimitSwitchesCable.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/LimitSwitchesCable-300x234.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/LimitSwitchesCable-150x117.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/LimitSwitchesCable-768x600.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 447px) 100vw, 447px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Now connect the<strong> Beam Break<\/strong> lines as shown:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><a href=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/BeamBreakConnected.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/BeamBreakConnected.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2095\" width=\"448\" height=\"312\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/BeamBreakConnected.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/BeamBreakConnected-300x209.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/BeamBreakConnected-150x104.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/BeamBreakConnected-768x535.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 448px) 100vw, 448px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"\/wiring-test\/\">Next: Wiring Tests<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>We are now ready to do the final assembly and wiring. First attach the Raspb